Cyber Claw:



Cyber Claw snapped at Drill Bit. "Don't touch me!" She backed up, 
baring her teeth fully. She turned her head, now hearing KitKat. 
Black Arachnia was here. Thank Primus. "Good," she said to her, and 
followed. She let out a growl at Drill Bit, warning him to keep his 
distance.
